Privacy Policy for the Media Links Chrome Extension

Effective Date: 26th April 2024

This Privacy Policy describes how the Media Links Chrome Extension (the "Extension") handles user data and privacy. By installing and using this Extension, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Data Collection:
The Media Links Chrome Extension does not collect, store, or transmit any user data. The Extension does not gather any personal information, browsing history, or other data from users.

Extension Functionality:
The Extension operates by interacting with the IMDb and Letterboxd websites to enhance the user experience. It does not collect or send any data from these websites to external servers or third parties.

Third-Party Services:
The Extension does not use any third-party services or APIs that collect user data.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the Chrome Web Store description and updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this Privacy Policy.

By using the Media Links Chrome Extension, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not install or use the Extension.
